    <S id="019S2">
        <FORM kindOf="original">sa azua milingan, ka vaik a maqinatsap a maɫetjelu a sema Tjuaqatsiɫay; manu qetsin a matsidiɫ nua se Tjuaqatsiɫay, aya.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">sa azua miɭiŋan, ka vaik a maqinaʦap a maʎəcəɭu a səma cuaqaʦiʎaj; manu qəʦin a maʦidiʎ nua sə cuaqaʦiʎaj, aja.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">sa azua milingan, ka vaik a maqinacap a maljetjelu a sema Tjuaqaciljay; manu qecin a macidilj nua se Tjuaqaciljay, aya.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">sa azua miɣiŋan, ka vaik a maqinaʦap a maʎəʦəɣu a səma ʦuaqaʦiʎaj; manu qəʦin a maʦidiʎ nua sə ʦuaqaʦiʎaj, aja.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">As for those treasures, three people went to Tjuaqatsiɫay to hunt heads, and one was killed by the Tjuaqatsiɫay people, they say.</TRANSL>
